HEADWORD: Mazard
<hw>Maz"ard</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>merise</ets> a wild cherry.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A kind of
small black cherry.</def>⟦br⟧
