==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Mazard
<hw>Maz"ard</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Prob. fr. <ets>mazer</ets>, the
head being compared to a large goblet.]</ety> <def>The jaw; the head or
skull.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mazard</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
